author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Are today's windshields are too strong for breaking in an emergency? Would it have been considered fair play to employ manufactured paintballs in the Painting with Explosives build? In this live stream excerpt Adam Savage answers these MythBusters-related questions from Tested members Ben L and Enduroance, whom we thank for their support! Do you keep a device in your car for breaking windows underwater?

@theslowmoguys: How fast does glass crack? https://youtu.be/GIMVge5TYz4
NPU vs GPU: https://youtu.be/WmW6SD-EHVY
00:00 Underwater Car
03:35 Fair play in Painting with Explosives
